Edit Image Data

To edit the Image select the Edit action

The Image opens in Edit mode. In Edit mode of the Image you can:

  1. Add additional sections and text at the landing page
  2. Format the free text by using the document formatting controls at the top of the page or add additional widgets to present additional data in the selected tab

Once open for editing the Image becomes locked for editing by other system users. All other user will be able to edit the Image when you save it.

      3. To save the Image press the Save button.
